name: Multi-AMP Engineering Sdn
overview:
Multi-AMP Engineering Sdn Bhd engages in trading, retailing, whole selling, designing, and building audio visual, sound reinforcement, and vision recording equipment for commercial and industrial use. The company offers public address systems, MATV/SMATV systems, nurse call systems, sound reinforcement systems, audio visual systems, card access systems, and PABX systems. It also provides security and CCTV systems, smart home and burglar alarm systems, stage lighting and stage curtain systems, conference and simultaneous interpretation systems, hotel bedside panel and key tag systems, and structure cabling systems, as well as video and audio intercom systems.

The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Seri Kembangan, Malaysia. Multi-AMP Engineering Sdn Bhd operates as a subsidiary of Tee International Ltd.
